    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "To clarify that,\r\nif we start without the weekly releases,\r\nwe're going to run `yarn release:prepare` on our local machine and it requires us to have a `.env` file with `GITHUB_TOKEN` in it.\r\n\r\n(And we don't need `NPM_AUTH_TOKEN` on our local machine because it will be taken care of by CircleCI.)\r\n\r\nI will give you all a simple guide again later when it's time.",
